BlockSource: http://www.rsssf.com/tablest/torino-vercelli-braztrip14.html
Season: 1914
Competition: Friendly

*South American Trip of Torino and Pro Vercelli in 1914
*
*Torino was invited for LPF (São Paulo professional league) to play some friendlies
*against his teams. Some days after, APEA and AMEA (respectively São Paulo and Rio de
*Janeiro amateur leagues) "answered" inviting Pro Vercelli to play friendlies against
*their teams.

*Matches played by Torino

8/9/1914; CA Internacional; 0-6; Torino                                 
Torino: Morando, Capra, Backmann - Valombra, Peterli, Lovati - Di Bernardi, Mosso III, Mosso I, Tirone, Arione, Mosso II.

8/12/1914; Foreign Players of LPF League XI; 1-5; Torino                   
*[b] the Foreign Players XI was formed basically by players from SC Germânia.

8/15/1914; SC Corinthians Paulista; 0-3; Torino                            
; Arione III (pk), Di Bernardi, Arione III
Corinthians: Casemiro do Amaral (Sebastião), Fúlvio, Casemiro González - Police, Bianco, César Nunes - Américo, Peres, Amílcar, Apparício e Neco.
Torino: Morando, Capra, Backmann - Valombra, Peterli, Lovati - Di Bernardi,Mosso III, Tomaselli, Arione III, Arione I.


8/18/1914; LPF League XI; 1-7; Torino         
*  [0-7?]

8/22/1914; SC Corinthians Paulista; 1-2; Torino             
                Américo ; Mosso II, Di Bernardi
Corinthians: Sebastião, Fúlvio, Casemiro González - Police, Bianco, César Nunes - Américo, Peres, Amílcar, Apparício e Neco.
Torino: Morando, Capra, Backmann - Valombra, Peterli, Lovati - Di Bernardi, Mosso II, Tirone, Arione III, Arione II.

8/25/1914; SC Luzitano; 0-3; Torino

*After these matches, Torino travelled to Buenos Aires.


9/1/1914; Argentina; 2-1; Torino
Alberto Marcovecchio, Alberto Marcovecchio ; Mosso

; Racing Club; 1-0; Torino
Alberto Ohaco;

; Argentina League XI; 0-2; Torino
; Mosso, Tirone


*coach of Torino: Vittorio Pozzo

*Matches played by Pro Vercelli

8/2/1914; CA Paulistano 1-0 Pro Vercelli                               
Hopkins;
Pro Vercelli: Innocenti, Binaschi, Valle - Dalmazzo, Milano I, Parodi; Ferrano, Carcano, Grillo, Rampini I, Corna.

8/3/1914; Combinado CA Paulistano/Scottish Wanderers FC; 5-1; Pro Vercelli

8/6/1914; Combinado AA Palmeiras/AA Mackenzie College; 1-1; Pro Vercelli

8/9/1914; Combinado AA São Bento/CA Ypiranga; 2-2; Pro Vercelli
Friedenreich, Friedenreich;

8/13/1914; APEA League XI; 2-1; Pro Vercelli             
Friedenreich, Millon ; Rampini I
: Rachou, O'May, Chico Neto - Gullo, Lagreca, Octávio Egydio - Formiga, Millon, Rubens Salles, Friedenreich, Hopkins.
Pro Vercelli: Innocenti, Binaschi, Valle - Dalmazzo, Milano I, Parodi - Ferrano, Carcano, Grilo, Rampini I, Corna.

*After these matches, Pro Vercelli travelled to Rio de Janeiro.

8/201914; Botafogo/Flamengo; 1-1; Pro Vercelli           
Luiz Menezes;
[g] line-up of Combinado 
Botafogo/Flamengo: Baena [Flamengo], Píndaro [Flamengo],Nery [Flamengo] - Villaça [Botafogo], Lulú Rocha [Botafogo], Gallo [Flamengo] - Arnaldo [Flamengo], Joca [Flamengo], Mário Fontenelle [Botafogo], Riemer [Flamengo], Luiz Menezes [Botafogo].

8/22/1914 Combinado Fluminense/América; 1-4; Pro Vercelli              [h]
Welfare ; Parodi, Rampini, Rampini, Ferraro
