8/23/1914 AMEA League XI; 1-1; Pro Vercelli                                  
Innocenti (og) ; Milano (pk)
*[i] according to some sources, the AMEA League XI was formed by players from CR Flamengo and América FC.

8/27/1914; AMEA League XI; 4-1; Pro Vercelli
Welfare, Ojeda, Welfare, Ojeda ; Ferraro



